!Bit!!Value!!Direction
|-
|0||1||North-East
|-
|1||2||South-East
|-
|2||4||South-West
|-
|3||8||North-West
|-
|4||16||East
|-
|5||32||South
|-
|6||64||West
|-
|7||128||North
|}
{{en/Ttdp|}} In TTDPatch this variable is for internal use only.

